# Embedded VF Programs Registry
# Each entry consists of:
#   - An ENUM_NAME line (uppercase identifier for the program)
#   - One or more indented shader file paths (lines with '/' and '.' are files)
# Entries are separated by blank lines.
# Lines starting with # are comments and are ignored.

DEPRECATED_CUSTOM_CPU_LINES
